		<h1 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
		<span style="font-weight: 400"><font size="5">American Sign Language: &quot;food and cooking&quot;</font></span><br>
		</h1>
		<blockquote><hr color="#000000" size="1" align="left">
		<font face="Arial">
		
		<p>Also see: <a href="food.htm">FOOD</a></p>
			<p>&nbsp;</p>
			<p>Vocabulary</p>

		<table border="1" width="590" id="table2">
			<tr>
				<td width="117" align="center">7-UP<br>
				AMERICAN<br>
				ANNUALLY<br>
				ANY<br>
				APPLE<br>
				APPLES<br>
