				BEEF<br>
				B-E-E-F<br>
				BEER<br>
				BEFORE<br>
				BLACK<br>
				BLT<br>
				B-L-T<br>
				BLUE<br>
				BLUE-BERRY<br>
				BOTH<br>
				BREAD<br>
				B-R-O-C-C-O-L-I<br>
				BROWN<br>
				B-U-R-R-I-T-O<br>
				BUTTER<br>
				CABBAGE<br>
				CARROT<br>
				CHEESE<br>
				CHERRY<br>
				CHICKEN<br>
				C-H-I-L-I<br>
				CHOCOLATE<br>
				COFFEE<br>
&nbsp;</td>
				<td width="152" align="center">COKE<br>
