&nbsp;<p>&nbsp;</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<p><br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet 51.A<br>
		<br>
		1. Question: GREEN SALAD-(tossed) &quot;throw into&quot; &quot;throw into&quot; (put in) WHAT?<br>
		Response vocabulary: LETTUCE, TOMATO, CARROT, ONION, CHEESE, B-R-O-C-C-O-L-I<br>
		<br>
		2. Question: FRUIT-S-A-L-A-D &quot;throw into&quot; &quot;throw into&quot; WHAT?<br>
		Response vocabulary: APPLES, ORANGES, GRAPES, WATERMELON, BANANA, STRAWBERRY, PEAR, PINEAPPLE, YOGURT-(Y-O-G-U-R-T)<br>
		<br>
		3. Question: WHAT-KIND PIE YOU LIKE?<br>
		Response vocabulary: LEMON, PEACH, APPLE, PUMPKIN, CHOCOLATE, BANANA CREAM, BLUE-BERRY, CHERRY<br>
		<br>
		4. Question: SALAD--(tossed) WHAT-KIND SAUCE-(dressing) YOU?<br>
		Response vocabulary: R-A-N-C-H, BLUE CHEESE, 1,000 ISLAND, O-I-L VINEGAR<br>
		<br>
		5. Question: DRINK WHAT-KIND YOU WANT?<br>
		Response vocabulary: SODA-(pop), COFFEE, TEA, MILK, BEER, WINE, WATER</p>

		<p>&nbsp;</p>

		<p>Practice Sheet 51.B<br>
		6. Question: WHAT-KIND SODA-(pop) YOU LIKE?<br>
		Response vocabulary: NONE, ANY, NOT-MATTER, ROOTBEER-(RB), 7-UP, COKE, PEPSI, MOUNTAIN D-E-W, ORANGE, DIET<br>
		<br>
		7. Question: POTATO BAKED, WHAT YOU &quot;throw on top?&quot;<br>
		Response vocabulary: CHEESE, ONION, C-H-I-L-I, BUTTER, SOUR CREAM…<br>
		<br>
		8. Question: YOUR COFFEE, SUGAR? CREAM?<br>
		Response vocabulary: I (don't) DRINK-(neg) COFFEE, BOTH, BLACK, &quot;little-bit&quot;<br>
		<br>
		9. Question: WHAT-KIND SANDWICH YOU LIKE?<br>
		Response vocabulary: B-L-T, COOK-(grilled) CHEESE, TURKEY, CHICKEN, NUT-BUTTER, JELLY, T-U-N-A…<br>
		<br>
		10. Question: HOT-DOG, YOU KETCHUP, M-U-S-T-A-R-D, WHAT-(huh)?<br>
		Response vocabulary: R-E-L-I-S-H, MAYO, ONION, C-H-I-L-I, CHEESE</p>

		<p><br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet 51.C<br>
		11. Question: WHAT-KIND B-U-R-R-I-T-O YOU WANT?<br>
		Response vocabulary: CHICKEN, BEEF, PORK, BEAN, CHEESE, SPICY<br>
		<br>
		12. Question: HAPPEN ANNUALLY, NOVEMBER THANKSGIVING, MANY AMERICAN EAT WHAT?<br>
		Response: TURKEY, H-A-M BAKE POTATO, D-R-E-S-S-I-N-G, Y-A-M…<br>
		<br>
		13. Question: YOU PREFER R-I-C-E BROWN (or) WHITE, WHICH?<br>
		Response: I DON'T-LIKE RICE, NOT-MATTER ME, LIKE BOTH, NONE-(neither)<br>
		<br>
		14. Question: WHAT-KIND PIZZA YOU LIKE?<br>
		Response: H-A-M PINEAPPLE, PEPPERONI, SAUSAGE, GREEN-P-E-P-P-E-R, MUSHROOM<br>
		<br>
		15. Question: YOU PREFER, GRAPE-F-R-U-I-T, WATER-MELLON, WHICH?<br>
		Response: DON'T-LIKE EITHER, NONE, BOTH SAME, NOT-MATTER ME.</p>

		<p><br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet 51.D<br>
		16. Question: BLT SANDWICH, what-MEAN B/L/T?<br>
		Response: BACON, LETTUCE, TOMATO<br>
		<br>
		17. Question: YOUR SANDWICH, WHAT-KIND BREAD YOU WANT?<br>
		Response: WHITE, W-H-E-A-T, R-Y-E, SOUR D-O-U-G-H<br>
		<br>
		18. Question: YOU LIKE PEPPER?<br>
		Response: DEPENDS, YES, NO<br>
		<br>
		19. Question: YOU BEFORE EAT CABBAGE SOUP?<br>
		Response: NEVER, NOT-YET, NOT SOUND GOOD<br>
		<br>
		20. Question: WHAT-KIND MEAT YOU LIKE?<br>
		Response: CHICKEN, B-E-E-F, P-O-R-K, BACON, HOTDOG, NONE I'M VEGETARIAN.<br>
&nbsp;</p>

			<hr><hr><hr><p>COOKING <br>
			EATING:<br>
			<br>
			DELICIOUS<br>
			EEK<br>
			FOOD<br>
			GREASY<br>
			MEXICAN <br>
			OK<br>
			SOUR<br>
			SPICY<br>
			STRANGE/ODD<br>
			SWEET<br>
			TASTE AWFUL<br>
			VOMIT-YUCKY<br>
			<br>
			BAKE<br>
			BOIL<br>
			COOK<br>
			DICE<br>
			FLIP-OVER-(cooking)<br>
			fry-(F-R-Y)<br>
			GRATE<br>
			MASH<br>
			POACH-(P-O-A-C-H)<br>
			POUR-over<br>
			ROLL-UP-(burrito)<br>
			SLICE<br>
			SPOON-DUMP-INTO<br>
			SPREAD-with-knife<br>
			SPRINKLE-CRUMBLE-over<br>
			STIR-(pot)<br>
			SPRINKLE/THROW-ON<br>
			GLOB-OF<br>
			ROLLING-PIN-(description)<br>
			PITCHER-(description)<br>
			ROLLING-PIN<br>
			PITCHER<br>
			<br>
			<br>
		Practice Sentences:</p><p>Question: YOUR EGG, HOW COOK YOU<br>
			Response: SCRAMBLED, (flip)-OVER EASY, (flip)-OVER MEDIUM, SUNNY-UP, <br>
			<br>
			Question: YOU LIKE FISH?<br>
			Response: SOMETIMES, NEVER, NOT OFTEN, DELICIOUS<br>
			<br>
			Question: YOUR HAMBURGER, WANT ON WHAT?<br>
			Response: KETCHUP, MAYO, M-U-S-T-A-R-D, CHEESE, ONION, PICKLE<br>
			<br>
			Question: YOU LIKE CORN C-O-B?<br>
			Response: YES, NO, A LOT BUTTER ME.<br>
			<br>
			Question: WHAT-KIND ICE-CREAM YOU LIKE?<br>
			Response: CHOCOLATE, VANILLA, STRAWBERRY …<br>
			<br>
			Question: WHAT-KIND SWEET YOU EAT?<br>
			Response: COOKIE, C-A-K-E, ICE-CREAM, CANDY, NONE, ALMOST NEVER<br>
			<br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet XX.A<br>
		1. <br>
		2. <br>
		3. <br>
		4.<br>
		5.<br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet XX.B<br>
		6.&nbsp; <br>
		7.&nbsp; <br>
		8.<br>
		9.<br>
		10.<br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet XX.C<br>
		11. <br>
		12. <br>
		13. <br>
		14. <br>
		15. <br>
		<br>
		Practice Sheet XX.D<br>
		16. <br>
		17. <br>
		18. <br>
		19. <br>
		20. <br>
		<br>
		Notes:&nbsp; </p>

			</font>
